  "title": "🏋️‍♂️Fitness Trainer – $1,700 + Uncapped Incentives",
  "description": "<p><strong>🏋️‍♂️ Fitness Trainer – $1,700 + Uncapped Incentives</strong></p><p>📍 Locations: <strong>Multiple locations island-wide</strong></p><p>🕒 Work Schedule:<strong> 5.5-day work week (Mon–Fri, alternate Sat/Sun)</strong></p><p>💰 Salary: <strong>$1,700/month + uncapped incentives </strong>(sell PT packages)</p><p>🎓 Training: 1st month base salary at $1,400 while undergoingtraining</p><p><br /><br /><strong>✨ What You’ll Get</strong></p><ul><li>Full training provided by experienced fitness professionals.</li><li>Complimentary gym membership.</li><li>Variable bonuses & uncapped incentives.</li><li>Full medical coverage.</li><li>Clear career path in a growing fitness company.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>🌟 What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li>Guide members to reach their fitness goals with confidence.</li><li>Conduct follow-ups with potential members.</li><li>Actively engage and build rapport with new and existing clients.</li><li>Support a positive and motivating environment in the gym.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>💼 What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Willing and able to do sales (PT packages).</li><li>Enjoy working with people and helping them achieve their goals.<br /><br /><br /><strong>📩 Apply Now</strong><br /><br />Submit your resume to<br /><br />📧 Email : annabelle.koh@crew.sg<br />📱 WhatsApp : 86852564<br /> Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /> Annabelle Koh (R25158748)<br />Hrnet Ventures Pte Ltd - Crew by Hrnet<br />E.A.24C2435</li></ul>",
